Package modelling

Class DefinitionModeller

java.lang.Object
modelling.DefinitionModeller
public class DefinitionModeller extends Object
This class adds and updates the definition elements of the model, which are those blocks implementing the SystemDesignDescription (SysDD) or InterfaceDesignDescription (IDD) stereotypes.
Author:
fernand0labra
